data.description: This gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 full bath home is located in the perfect spot for all the growth coming to Sherman! A mile down the road to the new Sherman high school and only a few minutes away from Texas Instruments and GlobalWafers. There were many special touches and upgrades to this home when built. Open concept with granite countertops throughout. The layout is very functional and provides plenty of storage space. The back porch has custom curtains to enclose the porch for more usable entertainment space or leave them open to provide ample natural lighting into the expansive living room. This is a large corner lot within the newer Heritage Farms neighborhood and will surely make you feel right at home!
